org.lemming.interfaces

Interface Store<DataType>

  • Type Parameters:
    DataType - - data type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FastStore, NonblockingQueueStore, QueueStore, TransferQueueStore

    public interface Store<DataType>
    Store represents a repository of generic objects. Only a get, a put and an isempty class are provided.
    Author:
    Thomas Pengo
